dialog.text: Please don’t hurt me.
Why are you adventurers always trying to hurt me?
I’m not here to hurt you. I just need to get past you to find some girls who were kidnapped.
You adventurers are always trying to save damsels in distress.
It wasn’t my choice. I don't suppose you ate one of them. If you did it would make my job a lot simpler.
Of course not! I don’t eat people! Way too much cholesterol. I generally have a nice diet of seaweed and low-fat cave clams.
So what seems to be your problem?
I found a huge stash of delicious cave clams and well, I couldn't help myself. And now I have this terrible heartburn and can't bear to move.
Hmm. Perhaps I can help.
*plop plop. fizz fizz*
Ah, that’s better.
So what’s your name? Some sort of a monster in the darkness? A dark-ness monster? :)
*sigh* You’re right most people call me Nessy, which is a horrible and childish name. I hate it.
Plus I never talk to anyone, so I don’t really need a name.
How about Mr Darkness Monster?
Too formal.
Hmm. Well, how does Pikachu sound? That’s not childish at all.
No good. Copyrighted.
Instead of Darkness Monster I can just call you DM.
Hmm. I like the sound of that. DM: Ruler of Dungeons and Dice.
Dice?
Um.. never mind. I’m the DM from now on.
Sounds great. It’s been a pleasure talking with you, but now I must be leaving.
Of course, all those damsels to save. Well, take this whistle. If you need any help just give it a tweet.
I always respond to tweets. I’m really a chat bot like that.
received whistle
Thanks DM.
No prob!
This water is too deep to swim without scuba gear
